5:
Doesn't matter when we come here, 
it's always bustling.
8:
People believe they will gain fame and 
fortune by delving into the 
Kaleidoscope. More adventurers 
appear by the day.
11:
It's crazy that such a dangerous place 
is so popular. Remember last week? 
When that poor guy got stuck in 
there?
15:
Hello again, Little Miss Fire in the Hole! 
You're looking perky as ever!
19:
Of course! Every day is a good day 
when you've got power like mine!
21:
Wish you could share some of that 
pep with the rest of us.
28:
No, no. She's more like a local celebrity 
here in Palpebra. She burst out of 
a tunnel in the ground, hence her 
nickname.
33:
Oh, but we didn't take any offense to 
her antics. After all, without her, one of 
our missing explorers would never've 
been found!
44:
Haha, you're blushing! Can't take 
a compliment?
49:
O-of course I can! But we've got 
shopping to do now! Right, Stella! 
C'mon! This vendor looks like they 
have tons of cute stuff!
54:
Ah, very well. But, Clarisse, I do not care 
for clothing so much.
61:
I am not so knowledgeable about 
fashion...
66:
What! How do you get through the day 
without fashion? We have to fix this!
68:
You're such a lovely girl! You need an 
ensemble that matches your 
adorableness!
78:
Leave it all to me! I'll select the perfect 
outfit for you and make you cute as 
a button!
93:
Mmm... I think so?Then how about this 
one?
96: Is it intended to look menacing?
99:
Phew, who knew you would be so hard 
to shop for?
107:
What's with the apology? I love 
a styling challenge!
110:
I think I know what's going on here. It's 
hard to suddenly change up your 
style, right? Hmm... How's this?
114: A barrette? Oh. I think this could work.
119: Yay! In that case, it's on me!
127:
Of course you can, silly! It looks soooo 
cute on you, Stella!
135:
What's become of Stella? She's been 
staring slack-jawed into the sunset for 
hours...
138:
Mm... I think I wore her out during our 
shopping extravaganza.
142:
Nah, not at all. She just takes time to 
process cheesy, personal stuff.
148:
Thank you for today. When I wear this 
barrette, I will think of you.
156:
It was my pleasure, Stella! I'm just 
happy that you're happy!
160:
Let's go shopping again soon! That 
way we can really start your 
makeover!
164:
I would love to. But please refrain from 
selecting such tiny articles of clothing 
in the future.
